# .env.example — documents which keys exist. NEVER put real values here.
# Copy to `.env` for local use if needed; `.env*` is gitignored (except this file).
#
# IMPORTANT: the portfolio SITE itself needs NO keys to build or run.
# The live Content Repurposer demo is bring-your-own-key (BYOK): the visitor
# enters their own key in the browser and it is stored only in their
# localStorage — it is never read from these env vars or committed anywhere.
#
# The variables below belong to the TOOLS' own runtimes (see tools/*/README.md),
# not to the website. They are listed here only so the full key surface is clear.

# Onboard — used ONLY by the future `generate-variants` step (Phase 5, not yet built).
# The deterministic Phases 1–4 (the shipped CLI) require no key.
OPENAI_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Drift — runs in Google Apps Script, not in this repo. Its OpenAI key lives in
# the Apps Script project's Script Properties, NOT in this file. Listed for reference.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=   (set in Apps Script Script Properties, redacted from this repo)
